  <brief_title>Fiber-enriched Buckwheat Pasta and Glucose Variability in Patients With Type 1 Diabetes and Celiac Disease</brief_title>
  <official_title>Fiber-enriched Buckwheat Pasta Reduces Daily Glucose Variability in Patients With Type 1 Diabetes and Celiac Disease: an Acute Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
